name: Teefsnatcha
description:
The game was made for Global Game Jam 2023. 

Teefsnatcha

-----------

Orks don't care much about their roots but take orkish traditions close to their hearts anyway.

One of them is using teeth as currency. And as any ork knows bigger teeth have bigger roots planted into the jaws of bigger orks.

Collecting those teeth is a dangerous task but it is worth it for any ambitious work.

OS: Windows 10+

DirectX support is required

How to run

----------

Unpack

run Teef.exe

Troubleshooting

---------------

There are prerequisites in the archive. You might need to extract and install them

to be able to run Unreal Engine.
